igh-level domains (e.g. Science, Technology, Philosophy, Arts, Politics, Business, Health, Sports, Entertainment, Education)\n- Consider including relevant subfields/subdomains if they are strongly represented throughout the conversation\n- If content is too short (less than 3 messages) or too diverse, use only [\"General\"]\n- Use the chat's primary language; default to English if multilingual\n- Prioritize accuracy over specificity\n\n### Output:\nJSON format: { \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\", \"tag3\"] }\n\n### Chat History:\n<chat_history>\nUSER: \u041f\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0435\u0442\nASSISTANT: \n</chat_history>"}], "stream": false, "options": {"num_ctx": 20000}},7:headers;220:37:4:Host,26:host.docker.internal:11434,]36:12:Content-Type,16:application/json,]15:6:Accept,3:*/*,]40:15:Accept-Encoding,17:gzip, deflate, br,]44:10:User-Agent,26:Python/3.11 aiohttp/3.13.5,]24:14:Content-Length,3:910,]]12:http_version;8:HTTP/1.1,}6:backup;0:~17:timestamp_created;18:1784454263.1503944^7:comment;0:;8:metadata;0:}6:marked;0:;9:is_replay;0:~11:intercepted;5:false!11:server_conn;489:3:via;0:~19:timestamp_tcp_setup;18:1784454182.1487322^7:address;32:20:host.docker.internal;5:11434#]19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;18:1784454290.5180233^15:timestamp_start;17:1784454182.142151^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:cipher;0:~11:alpn_offers;0:]4:alpn;0:~16:certificate_list;0:]3:tls;5:false!5:error;0:~18:transport_protocol;3:tcp;2:id;36:23432e00-5f48-4c22-be1a-82da28f46f1b;8:sockname;22:10:172.17.0.3;5:58938#]8:peername;26:14:192.168.65.254;5:11434#]}11:client_conn;457:10:proxy_mode;41:reverse:http://host.docker.internal:11434;8:mitmcert;0:~19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;17:1784454290.517248^15:timestamp_start;18:1784454182.1411307^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:cipher;0:~11:alpn_offers;0:]4:alpn;0:~16:certificate_list;0:]3:tls;5:false!5:error;0:~18:transport_protocol;3:tcp;2:id;36:ebaffad5-57ad-486b-b495-ef008e38f62b;8:sockname;21:10:1